<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Donation Successful</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .donation-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .donation-box .amount {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .donation-box .campaign {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .info-section {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .impact-box {
      border: 2px solid #f5576c;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .impact-box h3 {
      color: #f5576c;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
      <h1>Donation Successful!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{donorName}},</p>
      <p><strong>Thank you for your incredible generosity!</strong> Your donation has been successfully processed.</p>

      <div class="donation-box">
        <div class="amount">{{currency}} {{amount}}</div>
        <div class="campaign">{{campaignTitle}}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="impact-box">
        <h3>Your Impact</h3>
        <p>Your contribution is making a real difference! Every donation brings us closer to our goal and helps create positive change in the community.</p>
      </div>

      <h3>Transaction Details</h3>
      <div class="info-section">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span><strong>Transaction ID:</strong></span>
          <span>{{transactionId}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span><strong>Campaign:</strong></span>
          <span>{{campaignTitle}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span><strong>Amount:</strong></span>
          <span>{{currency}} {{amount}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span><strong>Date:</strong></span>
          <span>{{donatedAt}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your donation is now supporting the campaign</li>
        <li>You can track the campaign's progress on our platform</li>
        <li>We'll keep you updated on the impact of your contribution</li>
        <li>A tax receipt (if applicable) will be sent separately</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Thank you for being a changemaker and supporting this important cause!</p>
      <p>Together, we're making the world a better place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 CareForAll. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Keep this email for your records.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
